{"tid":726427,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行山被雷劈】Ian暑假後升大學 父親為水務署總工程師","createTime":"2018-07-02T11:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T16:05:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd259489607c18e2ceb90b8bffb19b669d20e87","tid":726427,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:26:24.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山麥理浩徑下午發生雷劈奪命事件，18歲死者姓盧，英文名Ian。其叔公今日接獲警方通知，趕至醫院了解，他對Ian意外慘死感到惋惜及傷心。<br />\n<br />\n據其叔公透露，Ian生前於港島南島中學讀書，暑假後即將升大學。Ian為家中長子，非常孝順父母，他性格外向，喜愛戶外運動，經常約朋友行山、打棒球及踩單車。Ian的父母現時身在日本旅遊，今日得悉愛兒死訊後，立即買機票趕回港了解。<br />\n據悉，Ian的父親為水務署設計部的總工程師，負責水務工程計劃的設計及招標工作。<br />\n英基學校協會教育總監Adam Hughes表示，今次意外非常不幸，向Ian的家人及朋友致以最深切的慰問，並會提供一切所需要的支援和協助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180702/large/1530526620_5a03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180702%2Flarge%2F1530526620_5a03.jpg&h=020292a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180702/58391335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F58391335&d=nbPBpL95CC5kiLBe3I2%2Fd2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=eeb027e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F58391335&h=6064c21f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180702/58391335</a>"},{"pid":"797ed5cf015ecbbbd1d764eabde84f0c87bab1a1","tid":726427,"uid":29314,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"鉛水報應？"},{"pid":"0a17efea109a690fc430aae9dafd9bfdf473173f","tid":726427,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:30:56.000Z","msg":"劈到咁傷既 <br />\n反白眼 上額腫曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513e1d4abe3b5123c01345f9e8dbdc6bca552a80","tid":726427,